The '''Gümüşlük International Classical Music Festival''' is held in the small fishing village of [[Gümüşlük]], [[Bodrum]], on the south west coast of Turkey. It began in 2004 and between 2006 and 2012 was organised by ''Bodrum Klasik Müzik Derneği'' (Classical Music Association of Bodrum), founded in 2006 for this purpose.<ref>http://www.annalindhfoundation.org/members/bodrum-klasik-muzik-dernegi</ref> In 2016 the festival expanded its programming to include a dedicated guitar week, and a series of jazz concerts. The Gümüşlük Festival Academy is organised annually parallel to the festival.<ref>http://www.gumuslukfestival.org/tr/gfa/</ref>

